title: Warren Vache on Advanced Lessons on the Trumpet
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Warren Vache, accomplished musician, conducts an advanced lesson with a young horn player. He demonstrates how to incorporate a number of techniques to practice and improve.
fulltitle: Warren Vache on Advanced Lessons on the Trumpet
